  "readme_markdown": "[![](https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.state/Emojis)](https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/Emojis)\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/Emojis\"><img src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.state/Emojis\"></a>\n[![](https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.api/Emojis)](https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/Emojis)<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/Emojis\"><img src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.api/Emojis\"></a>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-description\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#description\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a>[Description]</h2>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/HighestDreams/Emojis/blob/main/icon.png\">\n<p>Use real emojis in your pocket-mine server!</p>\n<p>You can choose emojis to show above your head!</p>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-usage\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#usage\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a>[Usage]</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Put phar from Poggit into <code>plugins</code> folder</li>\n<li>Edit the config.yml file of plugin in <code>plugin_data/Emojis</code></li>\n<li>you can customize message & timer for emojis</li>\n  <li>To see list of emojis use this command:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>/emoji\n  <ul>\n    <li>Permission: Emojis.permission</li>\n    <li>Default: Op</li>\n  </ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Hope you enjoy using this plugin!<p>\n<h2>[Libraries]</h2>\n<il>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jojoe77777/FormAPI/\">FormAPI</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>",
